  "text": "A hybrid bidirectional LSTM-HMM system applied to phoneme recognition has proved as an improvement over unidirectional LSTM-HMM as well as traditional HMM systems. Bidirectional LSTMs have been experimented on the handwriting recognition problem, and were evaluated on both online and offline data, thus proving to outperform the state-of-the-art HMM based system [CITATION_1] .",
